SWITCH TO ROOT
    su -
ONCE ROOT, RUN 
    usermod -aG sudo vboxuser
CAN ALSO USE 
    whoami
    (or) sudo whoami
EXIT
    exit
WHO AM I
    whoami
IT SHOULD RETURN TO ROOT. IF IT DOES NOT GET RID OF THE PROBLEM, JUST RESTART THE VM, THEN
    sudo whoami
IF OK, IT WILL ASK FOR PASSWORD AND RETURN
    root
CARRY ON WITH INSTALLATION
